      "description": "This E46 M3 is an immaculate specimen featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six, complete with its factory-spec individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS system. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, precise engagement, paired with a limited-slip variable M differential for optimal power delivery. Chassis integrity is paramount; this unit has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive rod bearing service. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, and the exterior displays a flawless finish with zero oxidative wear. It\u2019s a turn-key collector-grade machine for the discerning purist.",
